snippet.title: Nara Makes Games - Episode 014 | The Mayor of Sanctuary Game Play Footage
snippet.description:
I would prefer you do not watch this video before playing The Mayor of Sanctuary. But a lot of people have expressed concern that they have not seen clear game play footage. So here it is! I hope this answers some questions about what TMOS actually is.

@incube8games @josephtomkinsmusic
